It's todays society.  Americans are weak minded.  Too many flower children raising kids or something.  I mean WTF is a TIMEOUT!?!?!  When I did something wrong my parents got out the BELT.  There was none of this child abuse garbage around.  Today you are lucky if your state has lethal injections.  What happened to the CHAIR???  If you had a gun cops USED to be able to SHOOT YOU.  And to KILL TOO!  Imagine that!  If someone broke into your house, raped and murdered your wife, slipped on the newly mopped floor she just finished and broke their ankle they COULDN'T SUE YOU!  And if they did they WOULDN'T WIN.   <IMG SRC="eek.gif" border="0">   There was no political correctness.  A hole in a street with a round metal cover over it was a MAN hole.  NOT a SERVICE hole.  Why?  Because it was NAMED that!   <IMG SRC="eek.gif" border="0">  A male nurse was a NURSE (If there ever was one) not an ASSISTANT.  Equality was an issue, but wasn't blown as out of proprtion as it is today.  Now I'm not racist or sexist, but I had a teacher once.  SHE was the ONLY person I EVER met who wanted TRUE equality.  Whenever equality was brought up in class we would talk about it.  Women in the class were always like "We have to work harder and this and that..."  Then she would say "When is the last time you payed for a guy's dinner on a date?  You have to accept the good with the bad.  Until you do you will never be equal."  I was watching the news the other day.  An "african american" woman was on.  She said all "african americans are suffering from post traumatic slavery syndrome."  (I'm serious about this.  I'm sure it's in a newspaper somewhere or something.  Maybe even do a search on the net)  Ok so what whites did to blacks was wrong OVER 100 YEARS AGO.  ALL THOSE PEOPLE ARE DEAD!!!!   The ONLY reason it is still an issue is because THEY MAKE IT SO.  They say they want payment for the suffering.  Now I'm sorry, but not only are those people who commited those acts dead, but my grandfather came over from Italy MUCH after slavery and he was treated practicly as a slave also.  I feel no need to pay back the black community for slavery.  Again I am not racist.  I have nothing against EQUAL rights.  But nobody wants EQUAL rights.  They all want BETTER than equal.  If I make $20 an hour I think the next guy who is just as qualified as I am should make $20 an hour also.  Whether they are black, white, orange, purple, blue, green, male, female, a combo of the two ect.  There are VERY few people in the world (at least that I have seen) that would accept that though.  Everyone wants more more more.  That leads back to greed and the lawsuit issue.  This country is now built on GREED.  It works greed, plays greed, eats gree, breaths greed and lives greed.  Prime example....  Gulf War.  Why does America play the big bad policeman? (Or police person if you want to be PC)  To protect investmints.  They are burning those people in OUR OIL!  We have to stop them!  Our gas prices will go up!  Do you think we really went to war to save those people?  Why were we in Vietnam?  To stop communism?  In a way.  We wanted to stop communism because of the money we would lose to it.  We didn't care about those people.  We wanted their MONEY.  We carpet bombed the hell out of that country and probably killed as many civilians as we did the opposing army.  Only reason we used smart bombs in the gulf was because we could never get away with that these days.  You kill one civilain in a war and your presidency is an evil dictatorship to the public.  You lose all your funding and have to stop the war which makes you look worse. That's why you have to make the war look good.  You have to make it look like you are saving so many lives and get in the public's favor.   Americans are spineless and the government is corrupt and money hungry.  We are long overdue for a revolution....  <IMG SRC="eek.gif" border="0">   Sorry for the rant.  This is my 36th hour up right now and I'm a bit testy.  Also the cause for my many spelling mistakes which I am too tired to even care about    <IMG SRC="tongue.gif" border="0">
